# Reference literature (post-roadmap bucket 3). Locally-held PDFs of the papers and
# textbooks the param headers cite — the retrieval list in docs/plans/post-roadmap-citation.md.
# NEVER committed: this repo is public and most of these are copyrighted (commercial
# textbooks, publisher PDFs). We cite them; we do not redistribute them. Citations must
# stand on their own bibliographic locus, readable without this folder.
sources/

# Godot front-end (Phase 8). The project lives in `godot/`; `.godot/` is the
# generated import/cache dir (never committed). The `.uid` files ARE committed
# (stable resource identifiers, Godot best practice). `addons/` is the staged
# third-party MCP plugin (prebuilt binaries, external tooling) — kept out of the repo.
godot/.godot/
addons/
